parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty brake sensor can prevent the vehicle from starting, as the car may not register that it is in park, which can lead to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the brake pedal will not engage
the green key light on the dash flashes
the vehicle is in park but the car is not registering it.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and acceleration issues can cause the vehicle to stop accelerating, leading to potential safety risks, especially in traffic or emergency situations.
symptoms: The vehicle stops accelerating
the service engine light and traction control warning light turn on
little acceleration occurs
the engine seems to overheat in hot weather
the battery acid leaks
causing damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature tire wear can lead to reduced traction, increased stopping distances, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The front tires wear out prematurely
the back tires look almost new
the tires are too worn to rotate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine compartment fires can cause severe damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Smoke or burning odor coming from under the hood
black smoke pouring out of the engine
flames erupting from the engine compartment
vehicle filling with smoke
windshield bursting out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden loss of power and deceleration can cause accidents, especially if it occurs at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: Vehicle decelerates without warning
loss of power
engine failure to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Non-Functional Burglar Alarm and Ignition Lock-out
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The absence of a functioning burglar alarm and ignition lock-out can leave the vehicle vulnerable to theft and vandalism, potentially causing financial loss and compromising safety.
symptoms: No alarm sounds when attempting to break into the vehicle
no ignition lock-out feature
armed indicator light on the dash is present
but no alarm sounds when the vehicle is locked and armed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Traction Control and Brake System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning traction control and brake system can cause the vehicle to lose control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
